if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人認為d景點靚過泰國嗰啲好多 起碼無咁商業化同無咁多遊客<br />\n<br />\n去親d餐廳服務態度都好好，本地人好多都好友善<br />\n好純樸 無遇過呃人<br />\n搭親uber都同司機好好傾<br />\n不過聽人講係cebu人先咁，Manila 就完全唔同"},{"pid":"54ebe8006f1626d05b31957632570545ac28826c","tid":290833,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T23:35:16.000Z","msg":"仲菲律賓？<br />\n你唔記得左旅遊巴人質單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"d912cb681b4b810369982c766728907d759d0b71","tid":290833,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:25:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲菲律賓？<br />\n你唔記得左旅遊巴人質單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n睇清楚標題先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8b2ff40b20e2196eb5a1212c22b4df484a6ba2","tid":290833,"uid":120151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:56:06.000Z","msg":"喺印度做過大半年野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b0849e2b5622c5c36d6034a5a08d16de7a3707","tid":290833,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:00:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e85567f1333ec190a05b00e3fbecfdd838db9844","tid":290833,"uid":28736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:03:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有無人見到印度2隻字係聞到有味..</span>..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca1cc5c062e392c8882248ad33993c33a473cd9","tid":290833,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:06:24.000Z","msg":"工人國D雞應該正D"},{"pid":"9b8fa7888593be63eae097113afcbebb74bc3adb","tid":290833,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"